{
  "page": "Roro Uhoris",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/50px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/75px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/100px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Captain</span><br />Roro Uhoris<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Blind Bastard</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/50px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/75px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/100px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Blind Bastard</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nCaptain of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Cobblecat\" title=\"Cobblecat\">Cobblecat</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyroshi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tyroshi\">Tyroshi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-sea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-sea\">Eastwatch-by-the-sea</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Roro Uhoris</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Tyroshi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tyroshi\">Tyroshi</a> smuggler and pirate, captain of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Cobblecat\" title=\"Cobblecat\">Cobblecat</a></i>. He was known as the <b>Blind Bastard</b> up and down the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a> though he was neither blind nor a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roro_Uhoris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Roro claimed that he could tell one port from another just by the way they smelled. Cities were like women, he insisted; each one had its own unique scent. <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> was as flowery as a perfumed dowager. <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> was a milkmaid, fresh and earthy, with woodsmoke in her hair. <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> reeked like some unwashed whore. <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a> was sharp, salty, and a little fishy like a mermaid should be.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He said the more seals on <a href=\"/index.php/Seal_Rock\" title=\"Seal Rock\">Seal Rock</a>, the luckier the voyage would be.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roro_Uhoris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Roro had sailed the <i>Cobblecat</i> past <a href=\"/index.php/The_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Wall\">the Wall</a>, into a hundred little coves that had never seen a trading ship before, and traded arms to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a> in exchange for furs and other precious goods. On his return south of the Wall, the <i>Cobblecat</i> was intercepted by a <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> fleet and escorted to <a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-sea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-sea\">Eastwatch-by-the-sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> There, Roro was executed on the deck of his ship for trading <a href=\"/index.php/Armament\" title=\"Armament\">arms</a> to the wildlings, and all the goods that he had received were confiscated.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roro_Uhoris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_54\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 54\">Chapter 54</a>, Davos V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Davos II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121700\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.070 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.279 seconds\nPreprocessor visited